# A study guide: Jason "Jay" Flack
**Jason "Jay" Flack ** is an award-winning urban folk expressionist artist, community leader, and speaker known as "The Appalachian Battery" from Johnson City, Tennessee. Known for his bold colors, strong black outlines, and emotionally charged storytelling, Flack explores themes of identity, race, and resilience in his art. 

### Key Sites
- [Jason "Jay" Flack](https://www.artbyjasonjayflack.com/)
- [Instagram](https://www.instagram.com/artbyjasonflack/)
  
