- Dreams Take Courage | Jason Flack | [TEDxJohnsonCity] (https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=JCdRyqELGdc)
- An interview with illustrator & Tri-Cities arts advocate, [Jason Flack] (http://hollerhousebristol.com/blogs/artist-spotlight/artist-spotlight-jason-flack)
